{
  "HITL_REQUEST": {
    "id": "promotion-strategy-001",
    "title": "30-Day Promotion Strategy to Boost Revenue",
    "risk_tags": ["finance", "ops"],
    "summary": "Drafting a comprehensive promotion strategy to enhance revenue over the next 30 days.",
    "tools_used": ["SQL"],
    "assumptions": [
      "The promotion will target top-performing categories and products.",
      "Sufficient inventory is available for promoted items."
    ],
    "evidence": [
      {
        "type": "SQL_FACT",
        "label": "Current Revenue",
        "content": "$1,862.53 in the last 30 days.",
        "reference": "Sales data"
      },
      {
        "type": "SQL_FACT",
        "label": "Revenue Share by Category",
        "content": "Electronics (25%), Fitness (19.6%), Outdoor & Garden (13.4%) are top categories.",
        "reference": "Revenue share analysis"
      },
      {
        "type": "SQL_FACT",
        "label": "Top Products",
        "content": "Wireless Charging Pad ($1,865.65) and USB-C Hub 7-in-1 ($1,698.36) are leading products.",
        "reference": "Top products by revenue"
      }
    ],
    "artifacts_preview": [
      {
        "type": "STRATEGY_PLAN",
        "format": "markdown",
        "content": "### Promotion Strategy Overview\n- **Objective**: Boost revenue by targeting top categories and products.\n\n### Revenue Baseline\n- **Current Revenue**: $1,862.53 in the last 30 days.\n\n### Top-Performing Categories\n- **Electronics**: 25% of revenue\n- **Fitness**: 19.6% of revenue\n- **Outdoor & Garden**: 13.4% of revenue\n\n### Key Products to Promote\n- **Wireless Charging Pad**: $1,865.65\n- **USB-C Hub 7-in-1**: $1,698.36\n\n### Proposed Actions\n1. **Promote Electronics**: Focus on high-margin items like the Wireless Charging Pad.\n2. **Bundle Offers**: Create bundles with Fitness products to increase average order value.\n3. **Limited-Time Discounts**: Implement time-sensitive discounts on Outdoor & Garden items to drive urgency.\n\n### KPI Targets\n- **Revenue Increase**: Aim for a 15% increase in revenue.\n- **AOV Change**: Target a 10% increase in average order value.\n\n### Risks and Assumptions\n- Ensure inventory levels are sufficient to meet demand during the promotion."
      }
    ],
    "controls": [
      {
        "id": "objective",
        "label": "Promotion Objective",
        "type": "select",
        "required": true,
        "options": ["revenue", "margin", "inventory_clearance"],
        "default": "revenue",
        "help": "Select the primary goal of the promotion."
      },
      {
        "id": "max_budget",
        "label": "Maximum Budget for Promotion",
        "type": "number",
        "required": true,
        "min": 0,
        "max": 10000,
        "default": "1000",
        "help": "Set the budget cap for the promotion."
      },
      {
        "id": "max_discount_percent",
        "label": "Maximum Discount Percentage",
        "type": "number",
        "required": true,
        "min": 0,
        "max": 90,
        "default": "20",
        "help": "Define the maximum discount percentage for promotional items."
      }
    ],
    "actions": [
      { "id": "approve", "label": "Approve" },
      { "id": "request_changes", "label": "Request changes" },
      { "id": "reject", "label": "Reject" }
    ],
    "on_approve": {
      "next_step": "Finalize the promotion strategy and prepare marketing assets.",
      "outputs": ["final strategy document", "marketing assets drafts"]
    },
    "on_request_changes": {
      "expected_input": "Specify changes needed in the strategy.",
      "regeneration_rule": "Incorporate user feedback and regenerate the strategy."
    },
    "on_reject": {
      "fallback": "Provide a simplified strategy or escalate for further review."
    }
  }
}
```

